                                                                      "path":  ".github/release.yml",
                                                                      "line":  21,
                                                                      "body":  "The configured release-note labels do not match the repository\u0027s established label scheme. The issue templates apply `type:feature`, `type:bug`, and `type:docs` (for example, `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request.yml:3` and `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/bug_report.yml:3`), but these categories only match bare labels like `feature`, `bug`, and `docs`, so normally labeled PRs will fall into “Other changes”. Add the existing `type:*` labels here or update the repository labeling scheme consistently.",
