                                                                      "path":  ".github/workflows/release.yml",
                                                                      "line":  44,
                                                                      "body":  "This step only checks the tag string before creating the public GitHub Release, while the actual SDK release gates in `publish.yml` still run separately and can fail later. A stale CHANGELOG/PYPI README or failing tests could leave a GitHub Release visible for a package that was not successfully published. Reuse the release guard/tests here or create the GitHub Release only after the publish workflow succeeds.",
